title: #92Noon! Suter/Gleeman/StumptheSnob/BirkBit
description: Wild D Ryan Suter kicks off the show, Aaron Gleeman from Ft Myers ends the first hour. Dave Sinykin & Jon Krawczynski in studio entire middle hour to chat sports and play "Stump the Snob." Matt Birk in studio most of the final hour on Vikings football!
